  <brief_title>Cocoa Polyphenols and Postprandial Metabolism in Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Postprandial Effects of Polyphenol-rich Cocoa Beverage on Glucose, Insulin, Lipids, Oxidative Stress and Inflammation in Type 2 Diabetic Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
